description.Name: description
description.Value:
Earthwing's newest topmount, the Hoopty 34, is sick! It's got everything you need and nothing you don't. Check it out:

http://absboards.com/?s=hoopty&post_type=product

34″ x 9.75″

- 26″ wheelbase, with ample wheel clearance
- Deep .625″ elyptical concave with gas pedals in back
- Rigid 7ply maple core
- Pre-cured composite weave base layer for strength, and dampening
